description:
EXPLORE WALES PASS Unlimited travel with weekday time restrictions for any 4 days in 8 days. The area includes the whole of Wales and extends eastwards to Chester, Crewe, Shrewsbury, Hereford and Gloucester. Buy this ticket online from the TfW website It is also valid on Traws Cymru bus services. 
      Bus travel and other discounted facilities are available on any day in the chosen period, even if that day is not selected for rail travel. A discount of 20% is offered by the Ffestiniog Railway. Other heritage railways may offer discounts: Dean Forest Railway; Fairbourne Railway; Ffestiniog & Welsh highland Railway; 
      Gwili Railway; Llanberis Lake Railway and Talyllyn Railway, contact them for details.
